            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Henja Frydman</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#frydmanH" start="3928.529" end="x">Three days we traveled by rail. Three frightful days. No air, no toilet.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3943.431" end="x">So what would you do about the toilet?</span>
