            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Henja Frydman</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#frydmanH" start="5663.446" end="x">Yes, that is what they say. We even had in our <a class="term" href="#vothG_block">block</a> delousing sessions. 'One louse, and you are dead.'</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
